== Overview ==
The Photonic Shields use a deeper field, making them inherently better against explosive blasts and laser penetration than the Baron series shields.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Photonic Shield can be bought in the workshop, or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
